{"tid":1781691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國戰線]小弟打算整記錄片","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T13:36:23.000Z","uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42bd17c27c679d3dafae24aa465b39ef93dabb7d","tid":1781691,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"事關上一個po沈咗，我決定再開多次<br />\n等小弟自爆一下先，我今年中三，英文OK，六月頭開始發夢到而家。咁作為一個半和半，我成日都覺得自己冇撚用，衝得又唔夠前，又唔夠和理非咁有米。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁有一日，我突然間諗到:呀！不如做個全英文記錄片喇！又可以以中立嘅角度俾鬼佬望下香港搞乜柒，廣告收益又可以捐俾有需要手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，上得嚟連登開po就唔止咁簡單喇。我想問下有冇ching有9/6開始到今日(13/12)嘅任何片？有嘅話可唔可以TG Contact我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />TG:gay_ge_guy<br />\n<br />\n記得較好私隱設定呀btw，呢度冇人想識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0178b7a854bacbb5c293a4461a7b00088149a6b","tid":1781691,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd34a2d91399ae6bba50310fc7323f62820f604e","tid":1781691,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9026fe3058ec6ff0e90bf65c5e06d6e1ba9b5c05","tid":1781691,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510710fa2e45c8db14a7a7e4ecaa76c957e10afb","tid":1781691,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"太多人整<br />\n又搞眾籌<br />\n可能整短片好啲"}]}